 drivers/spi/Kconfig      |   7 ++
 drivers/spi/Makefile     |   1 +
 drivers/spi/spi-ar934x.c | 235 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 243 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 drivers/spi/spi-ar934x.c

